<p><a title="Daniele Panozzo's homepage" href="http://cs.nyu.edu/~panozzo/" target="_blank">Daniele Panozzo</a> has been awarded an <a title="NSF CAREER award: Coupling Geometry Acquisition and Digital Fabrication" href="https://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/showAward?AWD_ID=1652515&amp;HistoricalAwards=false" target="_blank">NSF CAREER award</a> supporting his research project "Coupling Geometric Acquisition and Digital Fabrication". The goal of this project is to develop algorithmic foundations to tightly integrate 3D scanning&hellip;
